Stardoc is an "Acmeist"<http://www.acmeism.org> documentation framework. It allows you to write software in one of the following input formats:

* POD
* ReSTructured Text
* Markdown
* MediaWiki
* Socialtext
* HTML
* DocBook

Stardoc can convert any of those input formats to these output formats:

* POD
* ReSTructured Text
* Markdown
* MediaWiki
* Socialtext
* HTML
* DocBook
